{"tid":99420,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個教老豆老母用電話經驗","createTime":"2017-01-29T07:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T13:27:35.000Z","uid":69091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"568406d4a347c8cc6b65352def8873505382df71","tid":99420,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"有日我媽叫我教佢sd voice message比佢同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：你㩒實哩個公仔 唔好郁<br />\n媽：咁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我㩒實左啦<br />\n媽：咁我幾時講野呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：哎呀 你一㩒實就開始講野架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n媽：咁依家點算好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：你隻手指向上拉！！！<br />\n媽：下？？？<br />\n我：向上拉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌點知我媽sd左個錄音出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢同事之後同我媽講 乜你個女咁惡架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe73f1d3f96cdd1be91fad873ef22771bdad0fe9","tid":99420,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"唔係掛 <br />\n得我老母咁蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a38f2b45ad4ef3e9fca16e20775a0f5995444bc","tid":99420,"uid":62969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:13:34.000Z","msg":"我老母講一次就識<img src=\"/as